OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe conundrum of early     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fretirement                 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Despite the cost of living crisis, it  
OL,6, seems increasing numbers of people are 
OL,7, retiring early - so much so, in fact,  
OL,8, that a recent House of Lords report    
OL,9, found rising early retirement was      
OL,10, causing labour shortages. What is it   
OL,11, like to retire early and what happens  
OL,12, when people regret their decision?     
OL,14,FTwo months ago, after a 31-year career 
OL,15,Fas a police officer Cambridgeshire's   
OL,16,FChief Constable, Nick Dean decided it  
OL,17,Fwas time to retire.                    
OL,20,FHe wanted to stay on in post. His      
OL,21,Frequest was granted.                   
